  "slug": "frogvasion",
  "title": "Frogvasion",
  "description": "Frogvasion is a fabric mod that adds a variety of hostile frogs, custom items and blocks to Minecraft along worldgen and gamemechanics.",
  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/ea9a53ce7a224f1ea5e2655e721e32283594d4cf.png\" alt=\"Frogvasion\" width=\"600\" height=\"151\" /></span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><em><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The Basics</span></strong></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Get ready for a ribbiting adventure like no other with Frogvasion - the ultimate <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">fabric mod</span></strong></span> that will take your Minecraft experience to the next level!</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>This incredible mod adds a whole new level of excitement to the game, with a variety of hostile frogs that will challenge even the most seasoned players. With 8 unique custom frogs, each with their own special abilities and drops, you'll have to be on your toes to keep up with these slippery foes.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>But that's not all - Frogvasion also introduces exciting new worldgen and game mechanics, including custom structures and the elusive Frogvasium ore. With this rare material, you can craft a wide range of fun and useful items and blocks that will help you on your journey.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>And if you're feeling adventurous, why not try taming some of these feisty frogs and taking them into battle against minibosses and other monsters? With Frogvasion, the possibilities are endless!</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>So what are you waiting for? Join Frogvasion and experience Minecraft like never before!</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">For Frogvasion version 2.1, this mod requires&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib/files/4572400\">Geckolib 4.2</a><span style=\"color: #000000;\">,&nbsp;any version</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">higher does not require Geckolib.</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>For Minecraft version 1.19.3, this mod requires&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib/files/4282014\">Geckolib 4.0.3</a></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp;For 1.19.2, this&nbsp;mod requires&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #00ffff;\"><a style=\"color: #00ffff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib/files/4096665\">Geckolib 3.1.37</a></span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><em><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\">Introduction to the Frogs (for more info, view the 'wiki' tab)</span></span></span></strong></em></span><br /><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/f44b8c7696051f41a4928b50a079627e43a75500.png\" alt=\"Soldier Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">This is the <span style=\"color: #993300;\">Soldier Frog</span>, the most common frog of them all.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/8e47633dde4ff5aaeb6f9a44d8506b895499cd9b.png\" alt=\"Armed Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">This is the<span style=\"color: #993300;\"> Armed Frog</span>, he can shoot Tadpole Rockets out of his mounted cannon.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/b4e055c1cae4c283a13ba0c468c678345a963ff2.png\" alt=\"Tadpole Rocket\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">A <span style=\"color: #993300;\">Tadpole Rocket</span> is tiny and anoying, but weak and fragile.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/864c105977658ab7b9ba4b62811c0cd359c99c48.png\" alt=\"General Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #993300;\">General Frog</span> is a miniboss who can kill you easily if you aren't carefull.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/587ebcb563da781571897274ab0367a61eab48d3.png\" alt=\"Grappling Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Meet the <span style=\"color: #993300;\">Grappling Frog</span>. With its tongue of 8 blocks, it pierces trough everything in its path.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/4f99ab41b2c9b172f82373e225eb39409fcbe318.png\" alt=\"Growing Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">The <span style=\"color: #993300;\">Growing Frog</span> is no easy challenge, the more he eats, the stronger and bigger he gets.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/d2674a002c6742713b72cd66be45e56cb86a8e66.png\" alt=\"Explosive Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"201\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">The ability of the&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Explosive Frog</span> is quite logical as its name gives it away. It comes close and explodes.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/c4cea9c1b6425c84388ecca409d23cdea54a539c.png\" alt=\"Ender Frog\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">The <span style=\"color: #993300;\">Ender Frog</span> teleports while attacking, his weakness is water.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ok3lhS4/images/116dba30b1717bf6320e53fa2fea1922b1dd0ce9.png\" alt=\"Ice Frog\" width=\"221\" height=\"172\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">This is the<span style=\"color: #993300;\"> Ice Frog</span>, a dangerous Ice Spike-throwing enemy. Upon touching it you will recieve a freezing cold.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><em><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/s2LAWSMyGkI?wmode=transparent\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></em></span></p>",
